      "SummaryText": "ences.  Members of East Penn's Hazardous Materials Team have received training in accordance with 29 CFR 1910.120.  \n\nPLANNED SAFETY CHANGES\nPlanned changes in process at this point consist of review and enhancment to emergency response"
